   18            <h1 class="blue-h1">What We Do</h1>
   19:           <p class="justify">We're like a coding bootcamp, but free, and we cover more than just web development. Our full-time program is longer than most at six months, it's followed by job placement, and it's specifically for local women and non-binary femme adults in need. Companies partner with us to provide mentoring and to formulate apprenticeship criteria and the program. (See what else sets us apart in <a href="{{ url_for('render_faqs_page') }}">our FAQs</a>.)</p>
